#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_inputeventaction.rst:19
msgid ""
"Contains a generic action which can be targeted from several types of "
"inputs. Actions can be created from the **Input Map** tab in the "
"**Project > Project Settings** menu. See :ref:`Node._input "
"<class_Node_method__input>`."
msgstr ""
"包含作为可以从多种类型的输入目标的通用操作。可以从 **项目>项目设置（Project > Project Settings）** 菜单中的 "
"**输入映射（Input Map）** 选项卡创建动作。参见 :ref:`Node._input "
"<class_Node_method__input>`。"

