msgid ""
"The action's strength between 0 and 1. This value is considered as equal "
"to 0 if pressed is ``false``. The event strength allows faking analog "
"joypad motion events, by precising how strongly is the joypad axis bent "
"or pressed."
msgstr "动作的强度在0到1之间。如果按下为 ``false``，则该值等于0。通过确定游戏手柄轴的弯曲或按压强度，事件强度允许伪造游戏手柄运动事件。"

